      feat: add powershell (#568)
      
      * feat(lang): Add PowerShell language support
      
      Add semgrep pattern support for PowerShell via tree-sitter-powershell
      (airbus-cert/tree-sitter-powershell). Ellipsis (...) is supported in
      statements, expressions, and command arguments. Metavariables ($FOO)
      work naturally since PowerShell's variable syntax already matches
      the semgrep metavariable pattern.
      
      Uses a custom prep script because tree-sitter-powershell is the first
      upstream grammar in this repo to use ESM ("type": "module", export
      default). The prep script creates a CJS-compatible copy of the base
      grammar so our wrapper can load it via require().
      
